        <character name="pubescence" value="pubescent" modifier="moderately densely" />
      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="808.txt-5">
      <text>Heads in corymbiform arrays (flat-topped to rounded, often layered, sometimes incorporating relatively long, leafy, lateral branches, clusters of heads terminal on branches, some lateral branches nearly equaling or surpassing central portions).</text>
